  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is <strong>Posthaste</strong>; arcade-style, fast-paced rally racing game. Delivered by a solo developer, it aims to provide a challenging yet entertaining experience to its players. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Fundamentals of Posthaste</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost</strong> <strong>-</strong> Filling up over time, the Boost feature can give your car either slow or instant burst of acceleration depending on your choice, including Default (Instant), Snappy (Instant), and Burn (Slow).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.poster.avif?t=1773747685\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.webm?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.mp4?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haste Meter</strong> <strong>-</strong> <strong>No matter how much boost you use, you'll always want more power</strong>. Fill your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> by drifting and driving at high speeds. With your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> full, you'll be able to initiate <strong>ProBoost</strong>.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ProBoost</strong> <strong>-</strong> The <strong>ProBoost</strong> feature allows you to have a major 10-second speed boost, which becomes available after filling up your <strong>Haste Meter</strong>.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.poster.avif?t=1773747685\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.webm?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.mp4?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Configuration - </strong>Basic configuration options for changing the Boost mode and adjusting gear ratios are available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Mods - </strong>Simple modification options such as boost refill speed and lightweight chassis are included to give you an advantage which can be unlocked by driving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghost Replay -</strong> Race against the ghost representation of your previous/best attempts</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other currently available content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Stages </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Cars  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Steam Achievements to unlock</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is <strong>Posthaste</strong>; arcade-style, fast-paced rally racing game. Delivered by a solo developer, it aims to provide a challenging yet entertaining experience to its players. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Fundamentals of Posthaste</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Boost</strong> <strong>-</strong> Filling up over time, the Boost feature can give your car either slow or instant burst of acceleration depending on your choice, including Default (Instant), Snappy (Instant), and Burn (Slow).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.poster.avif?t=1773747685\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.webm?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/3e48c914bb0b6f383e74afd3ddaac43b.mp4?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Haste Meter</strong> <strong>-</strong> <strong>No matter how much boost you use, you'll always want more power</strong>. Fill your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> by drifting and driving at high speeds. With your <strong>Haste Meter</strong> full, you'll be able to initiate <strong>ProBoost</strong>.  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ProBoost</strong> <strong>-</strong> The <strong>ProBoost</strong> feature allows you to have a major 10-second speed boost, which becomes available after filling up your <strong>Haste Meter</strong>.   <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.poster.avif?t=1773747685\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.webm?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2576440/extras/d5d31333c4a9bed15492774a5581d546.mp4?t=1773747685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Configuration - </strong>Basic configuration options for changing the Boost mode and adjusting gear ratios are available.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Car Mods - </strong>Simple modification options such as boost refill speed and lightweight chassis are included to give you an advantage which can be unlocked by driving.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Ghost Replay -</strong> Race against the ghost representation of your previous/best attempts</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Other currently available content</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Stages </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >5 Cars  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 Steam Achievements to unlock</p></li></ul>",
